additional_info:
Version 3.0.7:
Coloured buttons (it's better to identify which one is "danger" and which one is "ok");
Fixed search bar (finally! welp, fixed for me, you wont see much difference);
Added more svgs (you wont notice some, actually the theme was made for desktop version);
I also fixed the delete/pin modal, it was ugly!
Added a cool icon for edited messages c:

Version 3.0.6:
SVG color changes;
Adapted to the new Emojis tab;
Fixed inputs

Version 3.0.5:
Updated to the latest version

Version 2.5.4:
Color changes;
A lot of new stuff, like pinned messages, context menu.

Version 2.5.3:
Activated switches are now more visible.

Version 2.5.2:
More organizated code (easier for me =));

Version 2.5.1:
Some bug fixes;
Colors adapted.
The Streamer mode background is now dark.

